channel.description:

[center][center][u][b]FEATURES[/b][/u] 525 Interface Working Orbs Pk shop Donator Shop fun hill giants money making. Trimmed armor gives bonuses(such as g trimmed gives prayer bonus) Innovative pking maps. Bandos Armor Armadyl 80% God Sword Specs Dragon Fire Shield(special attack working) Donator Zone. Mystery box gives random rare(donator) Fully coded client(music plays when opened, nice interface, web link, chat effects) full working skills complete skillzone stable economy Leprechaun Money Making[/center][/center]
[u][b]ABOUT THE PK MAPS[/b][/u] Okay the idea of this is that there are 3 Non-Donator Maps, Box Arena, Temple, and Castle. Donators get, Quarry and Shade Hill added to that list. The point of them is to be like multiplayer maps which create a fun way to pk, different maps such as box arena is a rows of boxes which is ideal for mages and archers, Castle is great for Warriors and Pures do to the tight corners and thing hallways, Temple is short range fighting which is for quick combat. All this combines to make a interactive pking experience where your not subjected to the same old map.
